1
00:01:28,560 --> 00:01:29,480
Not bad, Yifan.

2
00:01:29,480 --> 00:01:31,120
Fang Group paid a fortune

3
00:01:31,239 --> 00:01:32,680
for Lot 6 across from our Wanhe Mansion.

4
00:01:32,959 --> 00:01:33,879
Let me have a sip.

5
00:01:38,799 --> 00:01:40,359
Now the flour costs more than the bread.

6
00:01:40,920 --> 00:01:42,799
Our sales office gets clients asking daily

7
00:01:42,799 --> 00:01:44,280
when Phase Two launches.

8
00:01:44,680 --> 00:01:46,040
They're all scrambling for our units.

9
00:01:55,400 --> 00:01:56,640
That's exactly what I was hoping for.

10
00:01:57,120 --> 00:01:57,920
Nice going, brother.

11
00:01:58,400 --> 00:02:00,040
Every step's gone exactly as you planned.

12
00:02:02,680 --> 00:02:04,079
For next week's agents' gathering,

13
00:02:04,840 --> 00:02:05,920
besides Su Yuanyuan,

14
00:02:06,159 --> 00:02:08,080
I invited every agent we've worked with

15
00:02:08,199 --> 00:02:08,919
to join us.

16
00:02:09,039 --> 00:02:09,719
Together?

17
00:02:10,080 --> 00:02:10,680
That's right.

18
00:02:11,479 --> 00:02:12,680
Our Phase Two right now

19
00:02:13,240 --> 00:02:14,599
is the hottest property on the market.

20
00:02:15,080 --> 00:02:16,759
We've got to bring in more bidders

21
00:02:17,199 --> 00:02:18,080
to drive up the price.

22
00:02:19,800 --> 00:02:20,560
You're absolutely right.

23
00:02:21,000 --> 00:02:22,719
I'm at Garden of Fortune Hotel next week.

24
00:02:23,080 --> 00:02:24,560
Let's see what tricks you pull.

25
00:02:38,319 --> 00:02:40,680
Why are you here? It hasn't started yet.

26
00:02:41,159 --> 00:02:42,439
I came to give you a heads-up.

27
00:02:42,840 --> 00:02:44,120
At the gathering later,

28
00:02:44,120 --> 00:02:45,400
there will be other companies

29
00:02:45,599 --> 00:02:48,080
after Wanhe Mansion Phase Two's agency.

30
00:02:48,800 --> 00:02:50,800
Chairman Zheng gave the sales agency

31
00:02:50,800 --> 00:02:52,280
to Xiao Yifan.

32
00:02:52,400 --> 00:02:54,240
You need to get that contract signed fast.

33
00:02:54,800 --> 00:02:56,039
What's the rush?

34
00:02:56,159 --> 00:02:57,319
Exclusive underwriting—

35
00:02:57,319 --> 00:02:58,960
can the other companies even handle it?

36
00:02:59,919 --> 00:03:01,520
Exclusive underwriting is more profitable,

37
00:03:01,879 --> 00:03:04,120
but the other firms aren't pushovers.

38
00:03:05,080 --> 00:03:06,000
Tonight,

39
00:03:06,000 --> 00:03:06,759
you absolutely must

40
00:03:06,759 --> 00:03:07,759
close the deal with Xiao Yifan.

41
00:03:08,680 --> 00:03:10,680
I've already booked the room, haven't I?

42
00:03:16,080 --> 00:03:16,840
Good.

43
00:03:16,919 --> 00:03:18,120
Then here's to you, Director Su—

44
00:03:18,280 --> 00:03:19,520
may tonight go just as you wish.

45
00:03:24,120 --> 00:03:25,879
Tonight I'll look absolutely stunning

46
00:03:25,879 --> 00:03:27,919
and be the center of attention.

47
00:03:28,360 --> 00:03:29,360
Xiao Yifan,

48
00:03:29,520 --> 00:03:32,039
I won't just win Wanhe Mansion's exclusive

49
00:03:32,479 --> 00:03:35,840
underwriting. I'll devour you whole.

50
00:03:36,360 --> 00:03:37,840
That project of his is pretty impressive.

51
00:04:05,639 --> 00:04:06,439
Yifan.

52
00:04:06,800 --> 00:04:07,520
Mr. Zhang.

53
00:04:07,719 --> 00:04:09,360
You all got here pretty early.

54
00:04:09,599 --> 00:04:10,520
We just arrived too.

55
00:04:10,919 --> 00:04:14,120
I was just introducing our new director.

56
00:04:15,919 --> 00:04:17,160
Hello, Ms. Su.

57
00:04:18,600 --> 00:04:21,279
Mr. Zhang, your team is full of beauties.

58
00:04:22,199 --> 00:04:23,879
Beautiful director?

59
00:04:24,079 --> 00:04:25,560
She's just a pretty face.

60
00:04:25,720 --> 00:04:27,959
A vixen stealing money from men.

61
00:04:28,519 --> 00:04:30,399
So she's Fang Bing's wife.

62
00:04:30,720 --> 00:04:32,240
Hmph, nothing special.

63
00:04:32,360 --> 00:04:35,199
She looks like a hostess with that makeup.

64
00:04:38,000 --> 00:04:39,040
Go ahead and pour.

65
00:04:39,399 --> 00:04:41,759
Ms. Su can drink anyone under the table.

66
00:04:42,360 --> 00:04:44,079
I can't drink that much.

67
00:04:44,120 --> 00:04:45,240
Mr. Xiao is the real heavyweight.

68
00:04:45,639 --> 00:04:47,519
Anyway, I'm not drinking today.

69
00:04:47,720 --> 00:04:49,120
If Ms. Su doesn't get drunk,

70
00:04:49,120 --> 00:04:51,040
then none of us stand a chance.

71
00:04:51,040 --> 00:04:53,199
Hahaha.

72
00:04:54,079 --> 00:04:56,480
Thank you all for coming.

73
00:04:56,480 --> 00:04:58,199
You're all our company's partners.

74
00:04:58,319 --> 00:04:59,480
Thanks for your support.

75
00:04:59,480 --> 00:05:01,639
Here, I'll down this glass first.

76
00:05:09,839 --> 00:05:10,759
Mr. Xiao, Mr. Han.

77
00:05:11,040 --> 00:05:12,480
You two are the hosts tonight.

78
00:05:12,720 --> 00:05:14,000
But I still want to say something.

79
00:05:14,120 --> 00:05:16,040
The marketing of Wanhe Mansion Phase Two,

80
00:05:16,399 --> 00:05:18,000
my company is very eager to cooperate.

81
00:05:18,480 --> 00:05:19,639
I hope you two bosses

82
00:05:19,680 --> 00:05:21,000
will give us plenty of opportunities.

83
00:05:23,120 --> 00:05:24,319
Everyone should already know,

84
00:05:24,720 --> 00:05:26,120
the Wanhe Mansion sales office

85
00:05:26,120 --> 00:05:27,480
is swarming with customers.

86
00:05:27,839 --> 00:05:29,040
Phase Two will definitely sell out.

87
00:05:29,439 --> 00:05:30,360
As for our company,

88
00:05:30,639 --> 00:05:32,399
we want to recoup funds quickly.

89
00:05:32,600 --> 00:05:33,240
So,

90
00:05:33,360 --> 00:05:35,000
this time, Phase Two

91
00:05:35,000 --> 00:05:36,439
will use exclusive underwriting,

92
00:05:36,560 --> 00:05:38,240
requiring a one-time payment.

93
00:05:38,439 --> 00:05:39,439
Today,

94
00:05:39,800 --> 00:05:41,319
it depends on all of you,

95
00:05:41,319 --> 00:05:42,680
who shows the most

96
00:05:42,680 --> 00:05:43,560
sincerity.

97
00:05:43,720 --> 00:05:44,519
Mr. Xiao,

98
00:05:45,160 --> 00:05:46,399
exclusive underwriting

99
00:05:46,399 --> 00:05:47,639
puts very high demands

100
00:05:47,639 --> 00:05:48,680
on our cash flow.

101
00:05:48,920 --> 00:05:49,759
However,

102
00:05:49,800 --> 00:05:51,879
for Wanhe's projects,

103
00:05:52,160 --> 00:05:55,040
we'll definitely keep cooperating.

104
00:05:55,240 --> 00:05:56,600
I'd like to toast you.

105
00:06:00,720 --> 00:06:01,920
Mr. Xiao,

106
00:06:01,920 --> 00:06:04,639
our company is also very confident

107
00:06:04,759 --> 00:06:06,319
in serving Wanhe.

108
00:06:06,720 --> 00:06:08,360
I'll drink three glasses to you.

109
00:06:08,839 --> 00:06:09,199
This...

110
00:06:09,720 --> 00:06:10,839
That's a very sincere offer.

111
00:06:13,279 --> 00:06:14,399
Wow.

112
00:06:15,480 --> 00:06:16,360
Alright, two glasses.

113
00:06:19,319 --> 00:06:20,079
Three glasses.

114
00:06:20,279 --> 00:06:21,040
What a drinker!

115
00:06:23,839 --> 00:06:26,600
Mr. Xiao, we'll drink to that.

116
00:06:26,959 --> 00:06:28,000
But,

117
00:06:28,000 --> 00:06:30,480
for the Phase Two sales rights,

118
00:06:30,639 --> 00:06:33,759
our company is very sincere.

119
00:06:34,720 --> 00:06:36,439
We can offer up to

120
00:06:36,879 --> 00:06:37,879
25,000 per square meter.

121
00:06:39,120 --> 00:06:39,800
Come, come, come.

122
00:06:40,079 --> 00:06:41,000
I'll drink first as a sign of respect.

123
00:06:45,319 --> 00:06:46,800
Mr. Xiao,

124
00:06:50,279 --> 00:06:52,319
Since Mr. Zhu is being so sincere,

125
00:06:52,680 --> 00:06:54,199
let me make my stance clear to you too.

126
00:06:54,720 --> 00:06:55,680
Our company

127
00:06:55,680 --> 00:06:57,240
will take on the second phase

128
00:06:57,240 --> 00:06:58,959
at 25,500 per square meter.

129
00:06:59,920 --> 00:07:00,560
Allow me

130
00:07:01,240 --> 00:07:02,360
to toast you three times.

131
00:07:02,959 --> 00:07:04,759
My company offers 25,800.

132
00:07:04,959 --> 00:07:06,480
I'll drink straight from the decanter.

133
00:07:07,120 --> 00:07:08,639
Alright.

134
00:07:11,759 --> 00:07:13,560
Thank you all so much for your support.

135
00:07:14,480 --> 00:07:15,680
I'm clear on the prices now.

136
00:07:15,879 --> 00:07:17,160
And I understand

137
00:07:17,480 --> 00:07:18,439
everyone's intentions.

138
00:07:18,720 --> 00:07:20,600
Let me toast you all once more.

139
00:07:24,480 --> 00:07:25,879
Ms. Su,

140
00:07:26,279 --> 00:07:28,399
with a beauty like you here,

141
00:07:29,040 --> 00:07:31,000
I'll have to drink a few extra today.

142
00:07:31,680 --> 00:07:33,319
Now, don't tease me.

143
00:07:33,759 --> 00:07:35,319
You already have a beauty by your side.

144
00:07:35,319 --> 00:07:36,600
And you still want to drink with me?

145
00:07:36,759 --> 00:07:38,720
I'd rather have a drink with Mr. Xiao.

146
00:07:40,279 --> 00:07:41,600
Yifan,

147
00:07:41,720 --> 00:07:43,879
we were colleagues over a decade ago,

148
00:07:44,240 --> 00:07:45,759
and now we're business partners.

149
00:07:46,040 --> 00:07:47,199
So tell me,

150
00:07:47,439 --> 00:07:48,759
how should we drink this?

151
00:07:50,199 --> 00:07:51,040
Mr. Xiao,

152
00:07:51,040 --> 00:07:54,000
I had no idea you two went back like that.

153
00:07:54,120 --> 00:07:57,720
Shouldn't you two do a Wedding toast then?

154
00:07:59,399 --> 00:08:00,759
Everyone here has known me

155
00:08:01,000 --> 00:08:02,240
for over ten years.

156
00:08:02,560 --> 00:08:03,279
As for this drink,

157
00:08:03,680 --> 00:08:04,360
let's all drink together.

158
00:08:05,959 --> 00:08:07,000
Ms. Su,

159
00:08:07,199 --> 00:08:08,360
what do you think?

160
00:08:08,920 --> 00:08:10,759
Yes, yes, yes.

161
00:08:30,639 --> 00:08:32,080
Yifan's in the Peony Hall.

162
00:08:32,320 --> 00:08:34,120
He is bound to get drunk with this crowd.

163
00:08:35,840 --> 00:08:37,559
Let me give Yang Hui a call.

164
00:08:38,840 --> 00:08:39,639
We're off.

165
00:08:39,639 --> 00:08:41,080
Bottoms up, bottoms up.

166
00:08:43,480 --> 00:08:44,000
Let's go.

167
00:08:44,000 --> 00:08:44,480
Take care.

168
00:08:48,440 --> 00:08:50,840
Have one more! Today's a happy day!

169
00:08:51,200 --> 00:08:52,519
Mr. Xiao, look.

170
00:08:52,519 --> 00:08:55,240
Ms. Su's toasting you. One more!

171
00:08:57,559 --> 00:08:58,320
This isn't even your limit.

172
00:08:58,480 --> 00:09:01,159
Let's drink straight from the decanter.

173
00:09:01,159 --> 00:09:02,039
Right? How about it?

174
00:09:13,320 --> 00:09:14,440
Mom, your phone.

175
00:09:17,159 --> 00:09:18,960
Dad must've had a lot to drink.

176
00:09:19,159 --> 00:09:20,320
You need to rein him in.

177
00:09:22,279 --> 00:09:23,320
It's Uncle He.

178
00:09:25,120 --> 00:09:25,639
Hello.

179
00:09:26,000 --> 00:09:26,840
Hello, Sister-in-law.

180
00:09:27,080 --> 00:09:28,360
I'm at the Garden of Fortune Hotel.

181
00:09:28,679 --> 00:09:29,679
If it's convenient,

182
00:09:29,679 --> 00:09:30,600
come pick up Yifan.

183
00:09:30,840 --> 00:09:31,559
Okay.

184
00:09:32,159 --> 00:09:33,440
I'll head over as soon as I finish up.

185
00:09:34,679 --> 00:09:36,399
Mom, are you going to pick up Dad?

186
00:09:37,320 --> 00:09:38,200
No rush.

187
00:09:38,559 --> 00:09:40,679
I'll finish this problem with you first.

188
00:09:42,720 --> 00:09:44,120
Mom, come with me.

189
00:09:45,000 --> 00:09:45,960
What is it?

190
00:10:01,679 --> 00:10:03,759
Mom, I picked this pretty dress for you

191
00:10:03,799 --> 00:10:04,919
to go pick up Dad.

192
00:10:05,399 --> 00:10:06,240
Why is that?

193
00:10:06,240 --> 00:10:07,360
You didn't notice?

194
00:10:07,360 --> 00:10:09,559
The way Auntie Su looks at Dad,

195
00:10:09,879 --> 00:10:10,879
her eyes light up.

196
00:10:11,120 --> 00:10:12,159
She likes my dad.

197
00:10:13,200 --> 00:10:15,440
She's been Dad's colleague for a decade.

198
00:10:15,440 --> 00:10:16,879
And now they're business partners.

199
00:10:17,480 --> 00:10:19,080
Sweetie, what are you thinking about?

200
00:10:19,120 --> 00:10:21,159
Mom, I picked this pretty dress for you

201
00:10:21,159 --> 00:10:23,000
to dazzle Auntie Su.

202
00:10:24,279 --> 00:10:24,879
Okay.

203
00:10:28,559 --> 00:10:29,039
Does it look good?

204
00:10:29,320 --> 00:10:29,840
It looks great.

205
00:10:30,840 --> 00:10:31,360
Such a good girl.

206
00:10:33,480 --> 00:10:34,480
You've had enough to drink.

207
00:10:35,639 --> 00:10:38,200
Mr. Xiao, let me take you to the hotel.

208
00:10:49,360 --> 00:10:51,320
When Yifan comes home late from a dinner,

209
00:10:51,320 --> 00:10:52,639
he always messages me.

210
00:10:53,559 --> 00:10:55,039
Why no message at all tonight?

211
00:11:01,720 --> 00:11:02,519
Yifan.

212
00:11:02,519 --> 00:11:03,679
There are cameras here.

213
00:11:03,679 --> 00:11:04,799
Come back to my room with me.

214
00:11:04,799 --> 00:11:05,360
Be good.

215
00:11:07,039 --> 00:11:09,399
Go home.

216
00:11:10,679 --> 00:11:12,039
Let me go home with you, okay?

217
00:11:23,200 --> 00:11:24,080
You two...
